# Canonical SHA-256 of the shared Universal Rules (the app='global' harness tier).
# Source of truth for cross-app rule-tier sync (see each app's Universal Rule #27).
#
# Computed as:
#   sed '/^> MCP Last Synced Hash:/d' .github/copilot-instructions.md | shasum -a 256
#
# Every app's bin/ci runs script/check_global_rules_sync.sh, which compares its
# local universal-rules hash to this value. Changing universal rules requires
# updating them identically in EVERY app repo AND bumping this hash in the same
# change — otherwise the unmirrored app's CI fails (its rules != this canonical).
a69962ee266a742cb970510f694aa2228a5b1a004c32e9bd07568ddb8485ddcd
